snippet.title: Amicia Michella【NIJISANJI / にじさんじ】
snippet.description:
Hi! My name is Amicia Michella and I'm Vtuber from NIJISANJI. You can call me Amicia, Cia, Amichon, or Amicin. I can speak both English and Indonesian, and my main livestream content is horror game and chill livestream! I also started to draw comic since 2022. You can find in my twitter using #AmicinComic hashtag!

Halo! Namaku Amicia Michella, Vtuber dari NIJISANJI. Biasa dipanggil dengan panggilan Amicia, Cia, Amichon, atau Amicin. Konten livestream utama Cia adalah livestream horror game! Cia juga ada komik di twitter yang dapat dicari dengan menggunakan hashtag #AmicinComic!
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
